PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780617775
OL,3,CRare Roman brooch found by metal
OL,4,Cdetectorist to go on show for first
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FHe added: "The basic idea of those
OL,8,Fsort of brooches is developed from
OL,9,Fones that were coming into the north
OL,10,Fof Britain in the Roman period, but
OL,11,Fwhat you see is in different areas
OL,12,Fthey adapt these, so local craft
OL,13,Fworkers take these traditions and
OL,14,Fadapt and change them, and this is
OL,15,Freally powerful.
OL,17,F"This is to do with adapting to living
OL,18,Fin this new world. You're taking the
OL,19,Fnew but adding bits of the old, bits
OL,20,Fof the familiar, and creating these
OL,21,Fnew objects that mark out who you are."
OL,26,@oD@KOUyD@AOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
