PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780617775
OL,3,CRare Roman brooch found by metal
OL,4,Cdetectorist to go on show for first
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FThe brooch was allocated to National
OL,8,FMuseums Scotland after being processed
OL,9,Fby Treasure Trove.
OL,11,FThe exhibition aims to "reshape our
OL,12,Funderstanding of Scotland's
OL,13,Frelationship with the Roman world" and
OL,14,Fwill look at the experience of a
OL,15,Ffrontier.
OL,26,@sD@XOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780617775
OL,3,CRare Roman brooch found by metal
OL,4,Cdetectorist to go on show for first
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FIt will explore the experiences of the
OL,8,Fsoldiers who tried to conquer the land
OL,9,Fas well as those of the communities
OL,10,Fwho lived around each military base,
OL,11,Fand the locals whose lives were
OL,12,Fthreatened by the Roman invasion.
OL,14,FThe fort of Inveresk, near Musselburgh
OL,15,Fin East Lothian, will be a key focus
OL,16,Fin the exhibition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780617775
OL,3,CRare Roman brooch found by metal
OL,4,Cdetectorist to go on show for first
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FThe world's most northerly temple to
OL,8,Fthe god Mithras known of in the Roman
OL,9,Fempire was situated at the fort and
OL,10,Ftwo "spectacular" altars from the
OL,11,Ftemple will be the centrepiece of the
OL,12,Fexhibition.
OL,14,FTickets for Roman Scotland: Life on
OL,15,Fthe Edge of Empire are now available
OL,16,Fand can be booked at nms.ac.uk/
OL,17,FRomanScotland
OL,19,FThe exhibition runs from November 14
OL,20,F2026 to April 28 2027.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@QO]
